{"tid":623084,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"搵人6月一齊去西藏","createTime":"2018-04-09T16:29:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-17T05:03:48.000Z","uid":1669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"674849569dd5ba0797c768ecd8272845e92e7e65","tid":623084,"uid":1669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T16:29:37.000Z","msg":"6月頭搭火車由廣州到拉薩<br />\n抖2-3日開始行程「阿里大北路線」<br />\n暫時有兩個人 希望搵多四個人包車<br />\n<br />\n路線如下：<br />\n<br />\n1: 羊卓雍湖-卡若拉冰川-江孜古堡-扎什倫布寺<br />\n<br />\n2: 日喀則-定日白壩-珠峰大本營<br />\n<br />\n3: 珠峰-崗嘎-薩嘎<br />\n<br />\n4: 薩嘎-仲巴-岡仁波齊<br />\n<br />\n5: 鬼湖-塔欽<br />\n<br />\n6: 古格王朝-札達-獅泉河<br />\n<br />\n7: 獅泉河-革吉-改則<br />\n<br />\n8: 改則-措勤<br />\n<br />\n9: 扎日南木措-文布南村<br />\n<br />\n10: 文布南村-尼瑪-雙湖<br />\n<br />\n11: 雙湖-班戈-納木錯<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n詳情可TG傾：peamanutd"},{"pid":"58baa8ef292e12f3566e6009724bcf50f8770d5d","tid":623084,"uid":57871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T16:40:54.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"e3b6c6ef3fee4cce2d38b52aac7f2527c5064bf0","tid":623084,"uid":90247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T19:43:52.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"d960b5c3806b9f9692b4563a5308d62c46855af8","tid":623084,"uid":26156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T01:43:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8da16e56bbb6deec3764b2d3095a79c906b2c141","tid":623084,"uid":1669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d960b5c3806b9f9692b4563a5308d62c46855af8","tid":623084,"uid":26156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T01:43:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T02:08:56.000Z","msg":"邊會有座廁比你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"629cc16420ff55f79487d9760d4add8a059c08b4","tid":623084,"uid":1669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T03:45:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.